{"tid":1534623,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Resign左AL補水其實係咪法例黎？","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:15:13.000Z","uid":43662,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"26d6e518e7a36927102ed702f62c63f66842005b","tid":1534623,"uid":43662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"上個月尾岩岩resign左<br />\nAL+補假加加埋埋都過20日<br />\n黎緊7號先出尾糧 法例黎講係咪一定要當人工咁出？<br />\n好驚到時乜9都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢依家仲想叫我返去做咁<br />\n<br />\n利申 做左1年幾"},{"pid":"42ae432d483bda526c87869764195811ce7fd6ef","tid":1534623,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67c90a142a87568a315c525ef5833ae4462cd2d5","tid":1534623,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"f991f93a401493b2f2d6d11d47f373528969f1e6","tid":1534623,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:29:24.000Z","msg":"一係補水，一係提早last day"},{"pid":"e7796884b1114345a41d0d92b135f5ab894e0485","tid":1534623,"uid":43662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f991f93a401493b2f2d6d11d47f373528969f1e6","tid":1534623,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:29:24.000Z","msg":"一係補水，一係提早last day"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"咁我都last day左<br />\n尾糧+淨低果20假 佢就一定要補水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"856d504b7b80862cbe0e8b35c00258921647c20d","tid":1534623,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7796884b1114345a41d0d92b135f5ab894e0485","tid":1534623,"uid":43662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f991f93a401493b2f2d6d11d47f373528969f1e6","tid":1